SUMMARY:
DELIVERY OPTIONS: Emmezeta offers home delivery for both standard and bulky items across all of Croatia, including islands, and a free in-store pickup service ('Klikni i preuzmi'). Parcel shop and parcel locker delivery are not mentioned. 
PRICING: Home delivery pricing is variable, depending on the quantity and dimensions of the products, based on a price list which is not detailed on the page. In-store pickup is free. 
PROVIDERS: Home delivery is handled by an unnamed 'external partner'. 
NOTABLE FEATURES: An express delivery option is available within 48 hours for locations within a 30km radius of a physical store, at a 50% higher price. The website also offers assembly services for an additional fee. 
WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is consolidated on a 'Dostave i montaže' page. It clearly outlines the types of services available (delivery, pickup, assembly). However, it lacks specific pricing details and does not name the courier service. Information on COD, weekend delivery, and parcel services is absent.
